198→const README_CONTENT = `# Sequant
199→
200→Structured workflow system for Claude Code — GitHub issue resolution with spec, exec, test, and QA phases.
201→
202→## Installation
203→
204→\`\`\`
205→/plugin install sequant@claude-plugin-directory
206→\`\`\`
207→
208→Or browse in \`/plugin > Discover\`.
209→
210→## Features
211→
212→- **16 workflow skills** for planning, implementation, testing, and code review
213→- **Automated quality gates** with test and QA loops
214→- **GitHub integration** for issue tracking and PR creation
215→- **Multi-stack support** (Next.js, Python, Go, Rust, and more)
216→
217→## Skills
218→
219→| Skill | Purpose |
220→|-------|---------|
221→| \`/spec\` | Plan implementation and extract acceptance criteria |
222→| \`/exec\` | Implement changes in a feature worktree |
